Package com.compuware.api.topaz.hostresources.zos

Interface IDefineGenerationDataGroupParameters

public interface IDefineGenerationDataGroupParameters
Parameters specifying the attributes to use when defining a new generation data group.

Instances of this interface can be created using the builder class DefineGenerationDataGroupParametersBuilder.

Since:
2.1.0
Version:
2.1.0
See Also:
DefineGenerationDataGroupParametersBuilder
Restriction:
This interface is not intended to be extended by clients.
